# BarBooks JS Full Stack Assessment


## Task 1: Logic & Unit Testing (15 min)
 - To verify this feature, follow these steps
 1. Go to your terminal or hit cmd + `
 2. cd backend
 3. npm run jest


## Task 2: Database Schema & Mock Data (5 min)
- to verify this feature, follow these steps
 1. Go to your terminal or hit cmd + `
 2. cd backend
 3. npx ts-node src/seed.ts => this will create a `data.db` on to your root file
 4. If you have sqlite viewer, you can simply click on it to view, but if not, you can run `sqlite3 data.db "SELECT * FROM orders"`
